==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto ''[[i-]]'' (indeterminate [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix) + ''[[-el]]'' (correlative suffix of manner or degree)

===Correlative===
'''iel''' (indeterminate correlative of manner or degree)

# [[somehow]]
#: Like other indeterminate correlatives, '''iel''' can be combined with ''[[ajn]]'', the adverbial particle of generality. '''''Iel''' ajn'' thus means ''[[anyhow]]''.

